
A jlu noq te xnaq´tzb´il, extzen mya tu´n t-xi q´et juntl majl, mya tu´n t-xi q´et juntl maj ex mya tu´n t-xi k´ayit. A u´j lu at toklen tuk´e Â©1972 Paramount Pictures. Noq tun tajb´en teya toj xnaq´tzb´il. MINTIʼ TUʼN T-XI QʼET TOJ JUNTZ TEMBʼIL.




MARIO PUZO'S
THE GODFATHER
tu´n Mario Puzo exttzen Francis Ford Coppola

TRANSCRIPT


tz´ib´en tu´n J Geoff Malta te www.jgeoff.com/godfather.html



N-okx kyxol qeju yek´b´il mya b´a´n n-chi kanet toj Epic .
Jun q´ij, extzen aju q´ij lu mya b´a´n tu´n t-xi´, k-okx tq´o´n qe yek´b´il te Saga ex Trilogía .

